Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And	I'm on Page 03 of Pelvis MRI
And	I select the radio button "Yes" in Contrast enhanced
And	I select the checkbox "Adverse reaction"
When	I select 'Limited urticaria' from 'Intensity / Type of adverse reaction' dropdown menu
Then	'Add new adverse reaction' button is enabled
And	"Occurrence of the adverse reaction" input field is enabled
And	"Duration of adverse reaction" dropdown menu is enabled
And	"Total recovery" checkbox is enabled
And	"Serious adverse event" checkbox is enabled
